00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:15.093
But you would feel horrible.

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:19.380
But when you're fasted, you're not hungry.

00:12:19.380 --> 00:12:21.990
So I do 72 hours,

00:12:21.990 --> 00:12:23.640
I don't do three and a half days,

00:12:24.540 --> 00:12:29.540
but I do 72 hours dry fasted
when I want to drop body fat.

00:12:29.970 --> 00:12:33.843
And like, that's awesome.

00:12:35.010 --> 00:12:37.110
But I also-
- I think a lot of people

00:12:37.110 --> 00:12:40.170
