00:26:13.590 --> 00:26:14.970
It's about the fact that you trigger

00:26:14.970 --> 00:26:16.410
the mental representation,

00:26:16.410 --> 00:26:18.030
you're now thinking of donuts again,

00:26:18.030 --> 00:26:19.950
you re-triggered the taste of donuts.

00:26:19.950 --> 00:26:24.330
So next time you think of
what to eat, donuts come up.

00:26:24.330 --> 00:26:27.390
Whereas if you never have
donuts for you, for example,

00:26:27.390 --> 00:26:28.500
if you think about what to eat,

00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:30.660
it's not like you're gonna
think, oh, shall I eat a donut?

00:26:30.660 --> 00:26:34.170
